OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud will burn back to the
OL,6,Fcoast this morning where it will
OL,7,Flinger through the afternoon in
OL,8,Fplaces. Otherwise dry and sunny. Warm
OL,9,Finland but cooler along coastal
OL,10,Fdistricts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine away from the east
OL,14,Fcoast. Then the rest of the night will
OL,15,Fbe dry with some mist and low cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FDry with some hazy sunshine
OL,18,Fbut low cloud will linger along the
OL,19,Fcoasts. Warm inland, coastal districts
OL,20,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
