OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart Friday, dry and brighter
OL,7,Fafternoon. Mainly dry and cloudy on
OL,8,FSaturday, chance of an early shower.
OL,9,FDry and bright on Sunday. Somewhat
OL,10,Fcooler inland than of late.
